<ul class="space-y-2">
<li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] text-red-800/80 dark:text-red-400/80">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">check_circle</span> At least 12 characters
                                    </li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] text-red-800/80 dark:text-red-400/80">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">radio_button_unchecked</span> Include numbers &amp; symbols
                                    </li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] text-red-800/80 dark:text-red-400/80">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">radio_button_unchecked</span> Upper &amp; lowercase
                                    </li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
